    <summary>Universal document format converter - shift between PDF, Word, HTML, Markdown and more</summary>
    <description>
Shift is a powerful command-line tool for converting between document formats.
Simply shift your documents from one format to another with ease.

**Features:**
* Convert between PDF, DOCX, HTML, Markdown, and text formats
* Apply custom CSS styling to HTML output
* Batch processing capabilities
* Command-line interface for automation
* Cross-platform compatibility

**Usage:**
```
shift document.docx --to pdf
shift report.md --to html --css style.css
shift file.pdf --to text --output extracted.txt
```
    </description>
